[{"id":"/sicpjs/2.5.1","tag":"TITLE","body":"2.5.1  通用算术操作"},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p1","child":[{"body":"\n    设计通用算术操作的任务类似于设计通用复数运算的任务。例如，我们希望拥有一个通用加法\n    函数","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"add"},{"body":"，其行为在普通数字上就像普通基本加法\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"+"},{"body":"\n    一样，在有理数上则像\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"add_rat"},{"body":"\n    的运算，在复数上则像\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"add_complex"},{"body":"\n    的运算。我们可以实现","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"add"},{"body":"以及其他通用算术操作，方法是采用我们在第 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"2.4.3","href":"/sicpjs/2.4.3"},{"body":"节中为复数实现通用选择器时所使用的相同策略。我们将为每种数字附加一个类型标签，并使通用\n    函数\n    根据其参数的数据类型调度到相应的包中。\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p2","child":[{"body":"\n    通用算术 \n    函数\n    的定义如下：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":1,"eval":false,"body":"function add(x, y) { return apply_generic(\"add\", list(x, y)); }\n\nfunction sub(x, y) { return apply_generic(\"sub\", list(x, y)); }\n\nfunction mul(x, y) { return apply_generic(\"mul\", list(x, y)); }\n\nfunction div(x, y) { return apply_generic(\"div\", list(x, y)); }"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p3","child":[{"body":"\n    我们首先安装一个用于处理\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"普通","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"数字，即我们语言中的原始数字。  我们\n    \n    为这些数字打上标记，\n    使用 \n    \n\tstring ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"\"javascript_number\""},{"body":"。\n      \n    本包中的算术运算是原始算术\n    函数\n    （因此不需要定义额外的\n    函数\n    来处理未打标记的数字）。 由于这些运算各接受两个参数，\n    它们被安装在以以下列表为键的表中：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"list(\"javascript_number\", \"javascript_number\")"},{"body":"：\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":2,"eval":true,"prependLength":95,"program":"chap=4&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAJgHQFY0EYBQuRRIA7CAewFcAnAYwFMAaUAWzIGcAXUAMwuJo4BLMsTagAFgEMAbnVCSeggB50AJqGIVmAIzpVQZbvKoBzLXWIc2aAmAAUAFXFze-ISNAAbQ