8V7x1CAA","body":"put(\"real_part\", list(\"complex\"), real_part);\nput(\"imag_part\", list(\"complex\"), imag_part);\nput(\"magnitude\", list(\"complex\"), magnitude);\nput(\"angle\",     list(\"complex\"), angle); "},{"body":"详细描述为何这个方法能够奏效。例如，跟踪评估表达式时调用的所有\n    函数\n    的过程，其中\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"magnitude(z)"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"z"},{"body":" 是下列图中所示的对象\n    \n\tfigure ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"2.24","href":"/sicpjs/2.5.1#fig-2.24"},{"body":".\n      \n    特别是，调用了多少次\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"apply_generic"},{"body":"\n    函数？每种情况下分别调度到哪个\n    函数\n    ？\n    ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"body":"\n      将上述代码行添加到包中会展开\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"z"},{"body":"，而这些代码行起到了传递的作用。\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"apply_generic"},{"body":"\n      将被调用两次。我们将用替换模型跟踪程序的求值过程。\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":8,"eval":false,"body":"magnitude(z);\napply_generic(\"magnitude\", list(z));\n// 在这种情况下：\n// type_tags = map(type_tag, list(z))\n// 计算结果为：\n// type_tags = list(\"复数\");\n// 且\n// fun = get(\"magnitude\", list(\"复数\"));\n// 由于添加了\n// put(\"magnitude\", list(\"复数\"), magnitude);\n// 因此 fun = magnitude;\napply(magnitude, map(contents, list(z)));\napply(magnitude, pair(\"rectangular\", pair(3, 4)));\nmagnitude(pair(\"rectangular\"), pair(3, 4));\napply_generic(\"magnitude\", list(pair(\"rectangular\"), pair(3, 4)));\n// type_tags = map(type_tag, list(z)) 的计算结果为 list(\"矩形\")\n// fun = get(\"magnitude\", list(\"矩形\")) 的计算结果为\n// z => math_sqrt(square(real_part(z)) + square(imag_part(z)))\n// 即 z => math_sqrt(square(head(z)) + square(tail(z)))\napply(fun, map(contents, list(pair(\"rectangular\"), pair(3, 4))));\napply(fun, pair(3, 4));\n(z => math_sqrt(square(head(z)) + square(tail(z))))(pair(3, 4));\nmath_sqrt(square(head(pair(3, 4))) + square(tail(pair(3, 4))));\n...\nmath_sqrt(square(3) + square(4));\n...\nmath_sqrt(9 + 16);\nmath_sqrt(25);\n5"}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 2.78","id":"#ex-2.78","child":[{"body":" \n    内部的\n    函数\n    在\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"javascript_number"},{"body":"\n    包中，本质上不过是对基本\n    函数","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"+"},{"body":"、","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"-"},{"body":"等的调用。由于我们的类型标签系统要求每个数据对象都必须附有一个类型，因此不能直接使用语言的原始基本函数。实际上，所有\n    JavaScript\n    实现都有一个内部类型系统，用于它们自身的内部操作。像\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"is_string"},{"body":"\n    和\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"is_number"},{"body":"\n    这样的基本谓词决定了数据对象是否属于特定类型。请修改来自章节 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"2.4.2","href":"/sicpjs/2.4.2"},{"body":"中\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"type_tag"},{"body":",","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"contents"},{"body":"以及\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"attach_tag"},{"body":"\n    的定义，使我们的泛型系统能利用\n    JavaScript的\n    内部类型系统。也就是说，除了一点之外，系统的运行方式应与以前相同，即普通数字应仅表示为\n    JavaScript\n    数字，而不是表示为对，其中\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"head"},{"body":"\n    为\n    \n\tstring ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"\"javascript_number\""},{"body":".\n      ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"body":"\n      以下修改将利用 JavaScript 数字实现：\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":9,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=2&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAJgHQFY0EYBQuAzAVwDsBjAFwEsB7E0AQwoobIAsB9FgcwAoKAngAcAplwbcANKDJ0KIkhQDOASlABvXKFAAnERSI76VJRxJEAtgCMRO3rMULlardtAB+UEIZU7AIgArBgA3BiUyHSohCjNLGx0-aQd5RVVXbQAuLx87QVFxKRk5J1UAblwAX0JSSlp6PLEeXgATJks1TW09AyNQE1jrWxa2ixV0j1BAkLCIqJjzQYTxrP7vX2GDUfHtTzYRBmaN9u3QLNsdGjtWzek-KwPQHm4RZtBry1AAWk-H4UaJPwqcpVYjkah0IqOVJHUYaVzdQzGUwLeIwsZuCbvCzLPqmNZXEbojETFhUAA2aJOZx0FwJN0m91eTxebxGXx+yRKgOBQA","body":"function attach_tag(type_tag, contents) {\n  return is_number(contents) \n    ? pair(\"javascript_number\", contents)\n    : pair(type_tag, contents);\n}\nfunction type_tag(datum) {\n  return is_number(datum)\n    ? \"javascript_number\"\n    : is_pair(datum)\n      ? head(datum)\n      : error(datum, \"bad tagged datum -- type_tag\");\n}\nfunction contents(datum) {\n  return is_number(datum)\n    ? datum\n    : is_pair(datum)\n      ? tail(datum)\n      : error(datum, \"bad tagged datum -- contents\");\n} "}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 2.79","id":"#ex-2.79","child":[{"body":"\n    定义一个通用相等谓词\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"is_equal"},{"body":"\n    用于测试两个数字的相等性，并将其安装在通用算术包中。该操作应适用于普通数字、有理数和复数。\n    ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":10,"eval":false,"body":"// 由 GitHub 用户 clean99 提供\n\nfunction is_equal(x, y) {\n    return apply_generic(\"is_equal\", list(x, y));\n}\n\nfunction install_javascript_number_package() {\n    // ...\n\n    put(\"is_equal\", list(\"javascript_number\", \"javascript_number\"),\n           (x, y) => x === y);\n\n    // ...\n}\n\nfunction install_rational_package() {\n    // ...\n\n    function is_equal(x, y) {\n        return numer(x) * denom(y) === numer(y) * denom(x);\n    }\n\n    put(\"is_equal\", list(\"rational\", \"rational\"), is_equal);\n\n    // ...\n}\n\nfunction install_complex_package() {\n    // ...\n\n    function is_equal(z1, z2) {\n        return real_part(z1) === real_part(z2)\n               ? imag_part(z1) === imag_part(z2)\n               : false;\n    }\n\n    put(\"is_equal\", list(\"complex\", \"complex\"),\n            is_equal);\n\n    //...\n}"}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 2.80","id":"#ex-2.80","child":[{"body":"\n    定义一个通用谓词\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"is_equal_to_zero"},{"body":"\n    定义一个操作，用于测试其参数是否为零，并将其安装到通用算术包中。该操作应适用于普通数字、有理数以及复数。\n    ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":11,"eval":false,"body":"// 由 GitHub 用户 clean99 提供\n\nfunction is_equal_to_zero(x) {\n    return apply_generic(\"is_equal_to_zero\", list(x));\n}\n\nfunction install_javascript_number_package() {\n    // ...\n\n    put(\"is_equal_to_zero\", \"javascript_number\",\n          x => x === 0);\n\n    // ...\n}\n\nfunction install_rational_package() {\n    // ...\n\n    function is_equal_to_zero(x) {\n        return numer(x) === 0;\n    }\n\n    put(\"is_equal_to_zero\", \"rational\",\n           is_equal_to_zero);\n\n    // ...\n}\n\nfunction install_complex_package() {\n    // ...\n\n    function is_equal_to_zero(z) {\n        return real_part(z) === 0\n               ? imag_part(z) === 0\n               : false;\n    }\n\n    put(\"is_equal_to_zero\", \"complex\",\n            is_equal_to_zero);\n\n    //...\n}"}]}]